        "x": 0,
        "y": 26
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Billable cost (est., USD/month)",
      "description": "ESTIMATE \u2014 not actual billed cost. Projected MONTHLY Cloud Run instance-based cost across the selected services, in USD/month. Derived from run.googleapis.com/container/billable_instance_time (ALIGN_RATE, summed across services = total billable instance-seconds per second), multiplied by a fixed per-instance-month price.\n\nPricing assumptions (us-central1, Cloud Run instance-based / Tier 1, as of 2026-06): vCPU $0.00002400 /vCPU-s, memory $0.00000250 /GiB-s. Every SDP Cloud Run service is provisioned at 1 vCPU / 512 MiB (0.5 GiB) per Terraform, so per allocated instance-second the cost is (1 \u00d7 0.00002400) + (0.5 \u00d7 0.00000250) = $0.00002525 /instance-s = $0.0909 /instance-hour \u21d2 \u00d7 730 h/month = $66.357 /instance-month. Request-count and networking/egress charges are NOT included.\n\nMath: USD/month = billable_instance_time(rate) \u00d7 0.0909 \u00d7 730 = billable_instance_time(rate) \u00d7 66.357. The rate is instance-seconds billed per second, i.e. the average number of billable instances; multiplying by the per-instance monthly price projects the run rate over a 730-hour month. Because all services share the same 1 vCPU / 0.5 GiB shape, a single scalar applies to the summed rate. If any service is later resized, this constant must be revisited. For true billed cost, set up a Cloud Billing BigQuery export and query it directly.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "stackdriver",
        "uid": "sdp-gcm"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 27
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "hide": false,
          "datasource": {
            "type": "stackdriver",
            "uid": "sdp-gcm"
          },
          "queryType": "timeSeriesList",
          "timeSeriesList": {
            "projectName": "solana-developer-platform",
            "filters": [
              "metric.type",
              "=",
              "run.googleapis.com/container/billable_instance_time",
              "AND",
              "resource.label.service_name",
              "=~",
              "${service_name:regex}"
            ],
            "groupBys": [],
            "crossSeriesReducer": "REDUCE_SUM",
            "perSeriesAligner": "ALIGN_RATE",
            "alignmentPeriod": "60s"
          },
          "aliasBy": "billable instance-seconds/s"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "calculateField",
          "options": {
            "mode": "binary",
            "binary": {
              "left": "billable instance-seconds/s",
              "operator": "*",
              "right": "66.357"
            },
            "alias": "Estimated cost (USD/month)",
            "replaceFields": true
          }
        }
      ]
    },
